        <h3>The Hang Time</h3>

      <p>The Hang Time is a full-screen vertical format for mobile that momentarily delays the user in an inline ad experience as they scroll through an article.</p>
        <p>A beta product was developed by our product team, but was rather difficult to work with. I suggested the idea of animations on a timeline that would 'scrub' with the Hang Time 'progress'.</p>

        <p>I developed a simple Javascript to run these animations, in a way that was easy to template so we could  produce pixel-perfect animation that would work across all device sizes.</p>

